Bryath you're misunderstanding the point.  If a MT takes the damage alone he takes 100% damage.  When a shielder is added the MT takes 50% damage and the shielder takes 75% damage.  This adds up to a total of 125% of the damage the mob was dishing out.  You take MORE damage spread across two characters than if it was left on one character.  That was the point.<br>
