</p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2F2F4F><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub14.ezboard.com/ubumbleroot.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bumbleroot</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>knows that Warriors are superior</span><br>  Posts: 32<br> <font color=#FF0000>(10/10/02 10:00:48 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2137.topic&index=34>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: meatshield ?</span><hr size=1> This is designed as a raid skill. One main tank and a warrior in each group. This makes it easier for the clerics to heal being that they have to focus primarily on the warrior in their group while they are using the Meatshield. <br>
The healing rotation on a Main Assist will more or less transfer to a Meatshield rotation in which the healers heal the warrior in their group.<br>
This should make it a little easier to heal on large raids as the main tank will be taking less damage then before. Supposedly on the test server the re-use time on this is 3 minutes. That coincides with the time that defensive lasts. There is a reason for this I believe. This allows the Main tanks to rotate.<br>
<br>
Here is the setup I believe this was anticipating.<br>
<br>
6 full groups- Each with a Main Tank capable warrior.<br>
I will label each group and each warrior as such A-group, A-warrior, B-group, B-warrior etc.<br>
<br>
A-warrior Main tanks for 3 minutes using Defensive.<br>
B-warrior uses Meatshield. A-warrior takes 25% of damage from the mob for 36 seconds.<br>
C-warrior uses Meatshield. A-warrior takes 25% of damage for 36 seconds.<br>
This is done repeatedly until E-warrior has used meatshield. At this point exactly 3 minutes have passed.<br>
<br>
B-warrior switches to Main tanking and then uses Defensive.<br>
A-warrior uses Meatshield and B-warrior takes 25% of damage.<br>
C-warrior uses Meatshield and B-warrior takes 25% of damage.<br>
This goes on until E-warrior uses meatshield.<br>
At this point exactly 6 minutes have passed.<br>
<br>
This process goes on all the way down to E-warrior. At the time this rotation is finished 15 minutes have passed. <br>
A-warrior is capable of tanking with Defensive again.<br>
<br>
