<br>
Incidentally, one poster above mentioned the problem of the uber-equipped MT taking less damage than the presumably less well-equipped meatshield.<br>
<br>
Basically, meatshield means that we can start to kiss goodbye to the idea of the monolithic uberguild MT who always gets the pick of the best gear, because several well-equipped warriors will be necessary for the tactic to work at its most efficient.  That doesn't sound like a bad thing to me.<br>
<br>
On the assumption that there's reasonable variation in PoP equipment choices, the characters can be equipped quite differently.  The MT who's taking less actual damage needs all the taunty weapons; the meatshield can just go for pure HP. <p><center><img src="http://www.bloodcult.net/Images/PyrpleSig.gif" border="0"></center></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2137.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a> <b>2</b> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showMessageRange?topicID=2137.topic&start=41&stop=52>3</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showPrevMessage?topicID=2137.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showNextMessage?topicID=2137.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2137.topic&index=40><img src=http://www.steelwarrior.org/forum/swaddreply.GIF border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.emailToFriend?topicID=2137.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.threadControl?topicID=2137.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2137.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub14.ezboard.com/fthesteelwarriorthearena.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=2137.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Cl